parameters.query:
SELECT distinct t.name,
CAST(substring(t.name from '\[(\d+)\]') AS INTEGER) AS catalyst_id,
concat(u.first_name,' ',u.last_name) as catalyst_name,
u.email, 
u.phone_number,
sc.name as SC_pic
FROM tags t
left join users u on u.id = CAST(substring(t.name from '\[(\d+)\]') AS INTEGER)
left join 
	(select distinct u.id, 
	t.name
	from users u 
	left join tag_taggables tt on tt.taggable_id = u.id
	left join tags t on t.id = tt.tag_id 
	where t.name like 'SC -%')sc
	on sc.id = u.id
WHERE 1=1
and t.name LIKE 'CT -%'
and t.name != 'CT - [5162] Jiun Test'
and u.email is not null
order by 2
